  "text": "In this study we nudge atmospheric winds to reanalysis, with the aim to disentangle the contributions of dynamics and thermodynamics to model biases in a GCM. Nudging has been used previously in model development and validation studies, which showed that the large-scale circulation is reliably adjusted to observations while the underlying model climatology is well retained [CITATION_1] ).",
